---
---

<section class="py-28 px-4 bg-[color:var(--color-background)]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)]">
        Loved by <span class="text-[color:var(--color-primary)]">Families</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)] max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Hear from families who've used LastRite to honor their loved ones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-[color:var(--color-surface-container-high)] rounded-card p-8" style="animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease forwards; animation-delay: 0s;">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-lg text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4 block">format_quote</span>
        <p class="text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)] italic mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          LastRite helped us create a beautiful tribute to my father. The process was simple and the memorial brought our family closer together during a difficult time.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--color-primary)]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[color:var(--color-primary)] font-bold text-sm">
            J
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)]">Jane Omuya</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)]">Nairobi, Kenya</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-[color:var(--color-surface-container-high)] rounded-card p-8" style="animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease forwards; animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-lg text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4 block">format_quote</span>
        <p class="text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)] italic mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Being able to share memories and receive condolences in one place meant everything to our family. It kept my mother's memory alive for everyone who loved her.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--color-secondary)]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[color:var(--color-secondary)] font-bold text-sm">
            M
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)]">Mary Kipchoge</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)]">Eldoret, Kenya</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-[color:var(--color-surface-container-high)] rounded-card p-8" style="animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease forwards; animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-lg text-[color:var(--color-primary)] mb-4 block">format_quote</span>
        <p class="text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)] italic mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          The fundraising feature helped us cover the funeral expenses and support causes that mattered to our father. LastRite truly is a digital sanctuary.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--color-primary)]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[color:var(--color-primary)] font-bold text-sm">
            D
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[color:var(--color-on-surface)]">David Kariuki</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)]">Mombasa, Kenya</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
